    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has browned, add your<strong> soy sauce</strong>, <strong>red chilli relish</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until sticky – this is your <strong>sticky ginger meat-free mince</strong></p>",
